message.content: <OUTPUT_TEXT>As a paralegal, I am tasked with preparing affidavits and other legal documents. This includes drafting legal correspondence and organizing and maintaining documents in both paper and electronic filing systems. It is essential to ensure that all documents are meticulously prepared and organized to support the legal team in effectively managing and presenting cases. Attention to detail and adherence to legal standards are critical in this role to provide the best possible support to clients and attorneys.</OUTPUT_TEXT>
